{"tid":93220,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞][哀傷的鹹片]《濕濡的女人》改 Juno《如髮》","createTime":"2017-01-24T08:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T08:47:08.000Z","uid":40429,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ec78210e784e4d5ebf088cd6743304a26467ce","tid":93220,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:52:43.000Z","msg":"原曲：《如髮》 - 麥浚龍 Feat.盧凱彤<br />\n作曲：Bert<br />\n填詞：周耀輝<br />\n編曲：陳珊妮 / 孔奕佳 / 王雙駿<br />\n監製：麥浚龍 / 王雙駿<br />\n<br />\n《濕濡的女人》<br />\n改詞：善莫善於水<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">（男）<br />\n<br />\n記不起你怎行近 <br />\n記不起我本來餘生 <br />\n只記住我身 <br />\n仍貼住你身 <br />\n在親像人 <br />\n像獸在狠<br />\n <br />\n記不起我怎行近 <br />\n毛孔卻已記得興奮 <br />\n拘束了無存在 <br />\n吻就吻<br />\n<br />\n毋需匿跡也算命運<br />\n放不底的通稱誘引<br />\n憑藉羞恥的舌沾滿一身</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">兩個身軀成癮</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下都不再似森林）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">兩個身軀震憾天昏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下也似抹了一片暈）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">因給予意義便興奮<br />\n誰人是受制那位到頭來沒有質問</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下也盼真假難分）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">兩個身軀成癮</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下都沾濕了的凡人）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">慾望本是正常終於共震<br />\n按照本能 <br />\n沿著你身軀 <br />\n深嵌<br />\n<br />\n毋需匿跡也算命運<br />\n放不底的通稱誘引<br />\n馴服也是劇情  <br />\n低首身貼身 <br />\n被套緊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">兩個身軀成癮</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下都不再似森林）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">兩個身軀震憾天昏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下也似抹了一片暈）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">因給予意義便興奮<br />\n誰人是受制那位到頭來沒有質問</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下也盼真假難分）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">兩個身軀成癮</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（前前後後上下都沒有靜過的呻吟）</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">因優勢去利導我身拉扯不停無限次接近</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（互傳著體溫）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">按照本能 <br />\n沿著你喘泣葬身<br />\n<br />\n即使有抱負抱住我一生<br />\n不想有抱憾抱住我一身<br />\n即管落力的交滲<br />\n我是人 <br />\n澄明在對岸 <br />\n慾望有海 <br />\n永沒渡輪<br />\n必須濕透我身</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（女）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">哪個身軀憐憫<br />\n哪個身軀勝利沖昏<br />\n因給予意義便興奮<br />\n誰人是受制那位到頭來被我質問</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">（前前後後上下親）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">哪有身軀憐憫</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">（前前後後上下都沒有動過的惻忍）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因優勢去利導你身拉扯不停無限的接近<br />\n按照本能 <br />\n沿著我身軀深嵌</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">按照本能<br />\n提示我<br />\n你是何人</span><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：一部哀傷的鹹片──《濕濡的女人》<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cinezen.hk/?p=6962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinezen.hk%2F%3Fp%3D6962&d=lpQc3k9qqopqOWg%2BlinPr0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d4a0f55e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cinezen.hk/?p=6962</a>"},{"pid":"423c98713199929e19c2b89e1b9aafcda48e633b","tid":93220,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"仲未夾到時間睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b004ddf37707a9928c2525e92c8d23bcd69af3","tid":93220,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"濕濕的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ab4d986bfeb136c649ce82da5ec78bed1cb4a0","tid":93220,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲未夾到時間睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網睇喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然入